Memory Layout: Consecutive allocated memory space, no overhead
Random access time: O(1) ->calculating the offset
Search time(unsorted): O(n)
Search time(sorted): O(logn) - binary search

array: a collection of elements
Arrays(class): https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/util/Arrays.html
Array(class): https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/reflect/Array.html

- arrays are objects
- array length is can not be changed after the array object is created

Exceptions/Errors:
ArrayIndexOutOfBoundException: not in valid range
NullPointerException: de referencing null
